      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's like i'm just stuck in this loop. everyone keeps telling me to \"hold on\" or \"stay strong,\" but they don't get it. they aren't the ones living in this hell. it feels like holding on is just a way to prolong the torture. if someone offered me a way to just... find that stillness you mentioned, to finally have some peace away from this... wouldn't that be a mercy? wouldn't that actually be kind?",
